{"title": "1MDB graft convictions put ex-Malaysia PM Najib out of the running if snap polls are called", "tags": "asia", "timestamp": "2020-07-28", "content": "KUALA LUMPUR - One thing's for certain now - Najib Razak will not return as Malaysia's leader should a snap poll is called.\nAs ridiculous as it may seem, before his conviction for graft on Tuesday (July 28), Najib was still a dark horse bet for his old job despite leading his Barisan Nasional coalition to a shock 2018 election defeat that was partly fuelled by his role in the billion-dollar 1MDB scandal."}